items.text: Group Course Detail — this dashboard includes detailed information about group members enrolled in a particular course. Use the navigation above return to the group detail view and choose in a different course, or to return to the multi-group view. Use the 'Activity & Enrollments' and 'Performance' tabs below to toggle between different enrollment details.
